object.customQuery:
select distinct
    c.policykey,
    c.claimnumber,
    c.catastrophenumber,
    c.catgroupdesc,
    c.claimnumber as claim_key,
    c.lossnoticenumber,
    c.claimstatuscd,
    c.claimstatusdt,
    c.lossdt,
    c.lossreporteddt,
    c.firstreportdt,
    c.claimtype,
    c.companyexaminer,
    c.catastrophename,
    c.sublosscausecd,
    c.losscausedesc,
    c.losscausecd,
    c.examinerproviderref,
    c.independentadjuster,
    c.doicomplaintind,
    c.insiuind,
    c.forrecordonlyind,
    c.nopaymentreason,
    c.claimexpert,
    c.remediationcontractor,
    c.causeorigin,
    c.plaintiffcounsel,
    c.defensecounsel,
    c.suitfiledind,
    c.subrogationind,
    s.resposibleparty,
    s.adversecarrier,
    s.totalrecoveryamt,
    c.reportedby,
    c.reportedto
from dbo.claimdetail c
left join (
    select *
    from dbo.subrogationdetail
    where openeddt is not null
) s on s.policykey = c.policykey
    and s.claimnumber = c.claimnumber
where c.roweffenddt = '9999-12-31 00:00:00.000'
    --and c.claimnumber like 'CLM%'
  and C.TypeCd = 'Claim' -- per grin-3133
    and c.claimstatuscd != 'Deleted'
-- per grin-3030
AND roweffstrtdt >= (SELECT etlbatchstartst FROM dbo.loadbatchetldt WHERE loadetltype = 'wf_msgr_views')
